{"tid":1507511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有荃灣居民自發清理楊屋道街市催淚彈殘餘化學物","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:40:36.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35dcd9e7c84539389583345dea1bf292fbd11a30","tid":1507511,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"荃葵青區昨日的遊行，其後演變成激烈警民衝突，警方施放多枚催淚彈，現場一帶至今仍遺留衝突過後的痕跡，有市民發起清洗楊屋道街市。<br />\n<br />\n下午約2時，約有6名市民響應行動，帶同水桶、梳打粉、手套、拖把等工具，自發清理街市內的扶手和牆身。<br />\n<br />\n行動發起人劉卓裕表示，昨日見到社區很多催淚煙，自己是土生土長的荃灣人，經常會到楊屋道買菜，擔心有殘餘化學物，希望盡力幫助清理社區。"},{"pid":"9896bf12665774e8f95a151cf273d5941152ac5e","tid":1507511,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=cf24f1f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"38955d040a267394ea0effa9a80d404df078363c","tid":1507511,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（推）香港政府最想見到嘅四個字唔係天下太平，而係......</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZ0GeKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZ0GeKq.jpg&h=b8655881&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PofKWXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPofKWXM.jpg&h=49ea8e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsrmZa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt